{"tid":1061318,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：朗誦式發言震驚彼岸 台灣「女孩」恐失戶籍 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-03-14T10:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T11:31:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8e15706bf33d8be17eadc2113b8c1e2672069668","tid":1061318,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:20:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190314/20633138\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190314%2F20633138&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpkqdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=8ec630f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190314%2F20633138&h=1c4021cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190314/20633138</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：朗誦式發言震驚彼岸<br />\n台灣「女孩」恐失戶籍 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190314/large/a1302a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190314%2Flarge%2Fa1302a.gif&h=e31bceb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n八方噚日報道過，喺台灣出生、擁有台灣戶籍、自稱係台籍港區（政協）委員嘅前中央政策組高級研究主任、劉兆佳嘅愛將凌友詩，以作狀到爆嘅朗誦方式發言，獲台上台下政協委員多次拍掌支持，左派全力吹捧，網民當笑話笑足成日！不過對台灣嚟講，呢個唔係笑話咁簡單！自稱「平凡台灣女孩」嘅凌友詩打住台籍身份，咁高調喺中共政協會議發言叫統一台灣，你估台灣政府會坐視不理？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內政部長︰等陸委會認定後處理<br />\n<br />\n台灣立法院內政委員會噚日原本審議《災害防救法》部份條文修正草案，由內政部長徐國勇出席會議，會議期間民進黨籍高雄市立委劉世芳鬧凌友詩，話凌友詩爸爸係國軍退休海軍副艦長，凌友詩話乜嘢中華人民共和國政府係中國的唯一合法政府、係中國政權的正統，完全對唔住中華民國前總統蔣介石，又問徐國勇凌友詩話願鞠躬盡瘁期待中共統一兩岸言論，有冇違反台灣法律。<br />\n<br />\n徐國勇答凌友詩言論實在不應該，至於會唔會以法律處理，徐國勇話應該朝向取消戶籍方向處理，但因為權責係陸委會，所以等陸委會認定之後，先輪到內政部處理，又話如果取消凌友詩戶籍，佢就連台灣居民醫健保險都會冇埋，到時凌友詩唔再算台籍，唔知仲有冇政協做呢？<br />\n<br />\n李八方  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n江湖滾熱辣 (馬龍)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：「關鍵缺席」補鑊 追打鄭若驊李家超 (李八方)"},{"pid":"46090fad738f5b5e2dc38e0fc6e76238476b8f0b","tid":1061318,"uid":11143,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:21:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9420bdae4f977884539273416a66f9fcf44d4497","tid":1061318,"uid":15924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:32:22.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"dfa7f3299c87da41cff79f7b82ff7354229398a3","tid":1061318,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"呢啲通常都冇事"},{"pid":"5a2712e5da9c6dfae8dc119f0b77f88aebd9ddae","tid":1061318,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"人地有綠卡"},{"pid":"2ebe0e08796914f79600ad1c4b744e4fda91c02c","tid":1061318,"uid":82532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:44:48.000Z","msg":"呢啲直頭通蕃賣國, 應以叛國罪處理"},{"pid":"4ffe0ad7ddd5194227f146247ddb3714744c56e5","tid":1061318,"uid":163350,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:46:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"661072e8666b149571bf38c372259ce19ea40a16","tid":1061318,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:57:34.000Z","msg":"想學李春姬?"},{"pid":"e9cb466963aa860f7eebde98a309410380a12a6b","tid":1061318,"uid":61018,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:00:02.000Z","msg":"佢仲有綠咭 怕咩"},{"pid":"5d0e8f339083da764a1c2022536c2a5574f38dfa","tid":1061318,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9cb466963aa860f7eebde98a309410380a12a6b","tid":1061318,"uid":61018,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:00:02.000Z","msg":"佢仲有綠咭 怕咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"所以特別&quot;愛國&quot;"},{"pid":"d7ac96e6b55f9e5921339d66dfd37234d5253bcd","tid":1061318,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ebe0e08796914f79600ad1c4b744e4fda91c02c","tid":1061318,"uid":82532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:44:48.000Z","msg":"呢